item.description: Join A Healthy Balance outside at Coletta Field (at the fountain) in Quincy for boot camp. If you have never been to A Healthy Balance, the first class is free! If you have been before, the drop-in rate is $15. Class is 45 minutes long. Please bring a yoga mat and a set of weights (we all share so just one size). Please arrive 5 minutes early to fill out paperwork.
